---
title: Spiced Duck Breast & Plum Sauce with Bok Choy and Buttery Mash
description: With Chinese New Year just around the corner, our chefs have created the perfect celebration recipe.  To get the skin crisp and golden and the meat lovely are juicy,  we’ve pan-fried the duck first before finishing it off in the oven. Served on a bed of creamy mash and a side of garlicky bok choy, drizzle over the sweet and sticky plum sauce for the finishing touch. This dish is pure luxury so although it might not take long to make you’ll want to savour every bite
